des:
CREATE HOME products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your vacuum and heater.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your vacuum and heater - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your CREATE HOME products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "CREATE HOME" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "CREATE HOME" app;
(3). You need to have some CREATE HOME devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "CREATE HOME" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "CREATE HOME" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "CREATE HOME" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "CREATE HOME", and you'll be navigated to "CREATE HOME" login page;
(9). Input your CREATE HOME account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
* Alexa,turn on robot
* Alexa,turn off robot

* Alexa,turn on heater
* Alexa,turn off heater
